text: Istamgulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Uralsky Selsoviet,Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 278 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 45 km from Uchaly, 3 km from Uralsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Istamgulovo
